{"tid":1503653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再即日轉活動 比多一兩日籌備好唔好","createTime":"2019-08-25T04:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T05:38:54.000Z","uid":27203,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2290ed2372448f9b90d26eedd3031af4ac606ddc","tid":1503653,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"我夠知機場係春袋啦 咁荃葵青係condom咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即日轉場一定唔夠人 <br />\n<br />\n就算今日講聽日搞都真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知大家嬲 但係有諗法就唔該揀個確實可行既日子先再籌備得唔得<br />\n<br />\n而家1/9空出黎你想搞咪搞 2/9罷課實質活動未有 淨坐百萬大道 你有好idea實有幾萬個學生同你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個陣元朗之後又罷工 728個晚又叫人罷<br />\n但係自己諗下有冇可能今日叫聽日罷 有幾多番工手足又請多左一假但係冇活動<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n唔想分化 有諗法就揀好日子做文宣</span></span>"},{"pid":"84685dd072ff54f6d1113ab1d9aea2151588399d","tid":1503653,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d91cd35de8099cb75d149644fc2780c928628432","tid":1503653,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"87b7d9382636432fd805eae505e0a0f7fc3f2fc2","tid":1503653,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:51:55.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"6970e402ad206ecbd1713330dc453570e634816a","tid":1503653,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"7aeaa2d85efffb370823360f7269adf09bbf72da","tid":1503653,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:5